xg2<- XGBTrainer$new(early_stopping = 50,
                     objective = 'binary:logistic')

xgb_model_2 <- GridSearchCV$new(trainer = xg2,
                                parameters = list(n_estimators = c(3000),
                                                  learning_rate = c(0.01, 0.1,0.5),
                                                  max_depth = c(5,2,10),
                                                  min_child_weight = c(5,10)),
                                n_folds = 3,
                                scoring = c('auc'))


xgb_model_2$fit(train_dat %>%
                  filter(invoice_issue_yearmonth != 202109) %>% 
                  select(adjusted_set_variables_2), "response")
converting the data into xgboost format..
